"use strict";(self.webpackChunkdoxa=self.webpackChunkdoxa||[]).push([[450],{6029:e=>{e.exports=JSON.parse('{"blogPosts":[{"id":"/2023/06/20/we-are-doxa-ai","metadata":{"permalink":"/2023/06/20/we-are-doxa-ai","source":"@site/blog/2023-06-20-we-are-doxa-ai/index.md","title":"We are DOXA AI \ud83d\ude0e","description":"At DOXA AI, our ultimate mission is to foster an international machine learning community best placed to tackle some of humanity\'s most pressing challenges, such as climate change. We passionately believe in the transformative power of AI to build a better world, and we hope you will join us on that journey.","date":"2023-06-20T00:00:00.000Z","formattedDate":"June 20, 2023","tags":[],"readingTime":2.23,"hasTruncateMarker":false,"authors":[{"name":"Jeremy Lo Ying Ping","title":"Co-founder & CEO","url":"https://jezz.me","imageURL":"/img/jeremy_lo_ying_ping.jpg","key":"jeremy"}],"frontMatter":{"title":"We are DOXA AI \ud83d\ude0e","authors":["jeremy"],"tags":[]}},"content":"At DOXA AI, our ultimate mission is to foster an international machine learning community best placed to tackle some of humanity\'s most pressing challenges, such as climate change. We passionately believe in the transformative power of AI to build a better world, and we hope you will join us on that journey.\\n\\nStay tuned for more! \ud83d\ude80\\n\\n\x3c!-- **We are DOXA AI**. --\x3e\\n\\n\x3c!-- At [Your Startup\'s Name], we are on a mission to harness the power of AI and machine learning for the greater good of society, the environment, and the economy. As co-founders, we are driven by a shared passion to address some of the world\'s most pressing challenges and pave the way for positive change.\\n\\nWho We Are: Pioneers of Purpose-Driven AI\\n\\nFounded by [Your Name] and [Co-founder\'s Name], [Your Startup\'s Name] is not just another tech start-up; it\'s a collective force of individuals committed to leveraging artificial intelligence to make a tangible difference. With backgrounds in [Your Backgrounds], we bring a unique blend of expertise and a shared vision to the forefront.\\n\\nOur Flagship Challenge: Revolutionizing Solar Power Forecasting\\n\\nOur journey began with a commitment to combat climate change. The inaugural [Your Challenge Name] focused on advancing solar power forecasting techniques to reduce carbon emissions in the UK. Through this challenge, we witnessed the incredible potential of collaborative problem-solving within the AI and machine learning community.\\n\\nWhy AI for Good Matters: A Global Perspective\\n\\nIn a world facing complex challenges like climate change, social inequality, and economic disparity, we firmly believe in the transformative power of technology. By fostering an international community of machine learning practitioners and enthusiasts, [Your Startup\'s Name] aims to assemble a think tank capable of addressing global issues through innovative AI solutions.\\n\\nBuilding a Community of Changemakers\\n\\nBut we\'re not just a start-up; we\'re building a movement. Our vision extends beyond competitions and challenges. We are creating a vibrant community where like-minded individuals can collaborate, learn, and contribute to projects that truly matter. Together, we believe we can drive positive change on a global scale.\\n\\nWhat to Expect from Our Blog\\n\\nAs we embark on this journey, our blog will be your go-to resource for insights into AI for good, updates on ongoing challenges, interviews with industry leaders, and deep dives into the latest advancements in machine learning. We invite you to join us on this exciting adventure as we explore the intersection of technology and social impact.\\n\\nStay tuned for regular updates, inspiring stories, and a front-row seat to the incredible work happening within the [Your Startup\'s Name] community.\\n\\nThank you for being a part of our mission to make AI a force for positive change! --\x3e"}]}')}}]);